1
00:00:06,166 --> 00:00:07,368
This is the toddler loop.

2
00:00:07,788 --> 00:00:09,772
A human classifies elements once.

3
00:00:10,414 --> 00:00:12,698
Clickable. Readable. Typable.

4
00:00:12,958 --> 00:00:15,062
The system learns the page vocabulary.

5
00:00:20,418 --> 00:00:22,024
Now watch what the agent sees.

6
00:00:22,868 --> 00:00:25,398
The sieve maps every interactive element on the page.

7
00:00:28,925 --> 00:00:32,591
Product titles. Listing prices. Seller ratings.

8
00:00:32,871 --> 00:00:37,260
The agent clicks through to a product, and the sieve re-maps the new page instantly.

9
00:00:47,884 --> 00:00:49,226
A completely different site.

10
00:00:49,686 --> 00:00:51,408
A state park reservation system.

11
00:00:51,928 --> 00:00:53,570
The sieve maps it just the same.

12
00:00:53,850 --> 00:00:55,152
Any site. Any layout.

13
00:00:55,692 --> 00:00:56,653
Zero retraining.

14
00:00:57,988 --> 00:00:59,390
The sieve sees the page.

15
00:00:59,911 --> 00:01:01,592
The glossary names every element.

16
00:01:01,812 --> 00:01:04,795
Your agent knows what to click, what to read, what to compare.

